room_title: Escape room "Mad Hatter's Asylum" by Know Way Out in Petoskey
room_description:
Enter a world of whimsy, twists, turns, dead ends and only one way out. The Hatter loves having guests at his un-birthday party! The only problem is they tend to never leaveâ€¦
It only takes 60 minutes for your brain to fully accept the mad world and be doomed forever to days of broken teacups, never-ending chess games and un-birthday parties. Unless you can outsmart the Hatter and decipher the clues left behind by other brave souls to help you escape.
